Introducing a rule-based chatbot designed to enhance your content processing experience. This tool adeptly generates keywords, summarizes text, and answers questions seamlessly based on your input paragraph. Utilizing a predefined set of rules, the chatbot swiftly analyzes and extracts essential information, providing concise summaries and relevant keywords. Whether you seek a streamlined approach to information retrieval or a quick overview of a text, this chatbot is crafted to efficiently cater to your needs. Engage with this rule-based chatbot for a refined content interaction, simplifying complex information with ease.
